      "text": "Estimation:\n\n100M DAU = 10^8\nseconds in day = 10^5\n\n10^8 / 10^5 = 10^3 = 1000 rps * 10k - 100k prs (peak)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Estimation:\n\n100M DAU = 10^8\nseconds in day = 10^5\n\n10^8 / 10^5 = 10^3 = 1000 rps * 10k - 100k prs (peak)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
